{"tid":2444203,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"夏威夷雞肉菠蘿薄餅","createTime":"2021-03-12T14:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T04:13:23.000Z","uid":393786,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"13f0a91a81715ee4f32ee1128f80447eaedd5f59","tid":2444203,"uid":393786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"大家一定要試,好簡單,薄批好好食,D麵粉發得好既話,大力壓扁個餅都無問題,整出黎都唔會死實實。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日星期六，可以試做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i8RRCyt3Tl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi8RRCyt3Tl0&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXIxzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=627b2192\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i8RRCyt3Tl0</a><br />\n麵團材料<br />\n中根麵粉250g<br />\n酵母1/4茶匙<br />\n鹽1/4茶匙<br />\n橄欖油1/2茶匙<br />\n水~180g<br />\n<br />\n配料<br />\n菠蘿適量<br />\n雞腿肉80g<br />\n番茄醬200g<br />\n糖 1/2茶匙<br />\n巴馬火腿適量<br />\n三色椒適量<br />\n芝士碎適量"},{"pid":"ae0f878de45a6b8261df15563c7daa3287368c04","tid":2444203,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"好似幾好食"},{"pid":"7dc247d6000c195c2e40921660781c9117522f2f","tid":2444203,"uid":393786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ae0f878de45a6b8261df15563c7daa3287368c04","tid":2444203,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"好似幾好食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"聽日試下，一定好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好簡單"},{"pid":"59a12469d342ab3f46e7d4090c0732674974036d","tid":2444203,"uid":27324,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"最好走菠蘿"},{"pid":"48509d9ee11ae4c63a80a0d93804eb18653e88fb","tid":2444203,"uid":174775,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,